node.text:
My 35th birthday is going up Sept 7th. And I have something very special! My best work!

Get on the waiting for my Legacy Bday Bundle with all of the program I have ever created! Over 6 programs at a regular price of $12,958. Get everything for $995. Only 100 will be available.

I’m excited to give this value. My birthday is a special day for me and I want to celebrate it with the 100 people that will be lucky enough to get my best work since 2008. Everything I know about social media, growth, and monetization online. 🖤💰 

Join the waiting list to be the first notified: 

Bit.ly/SpecBdayBundle

💫

node.text:
In this era of social media and instant gratification, it's more lucrative than ever to start a digital business that caters to the needs of your target audience.

The best passive income business to jump into in 2021 is a digital one. The internet revolution has created an era where every company needs some sort of online presence, and this means that there are endless opportunities for the savvy entrepreneur with little capital. Entrepreneurs can have their own storefront on social media or create product-based content under Youtube's Partner Program--which only requires uploading quality videos at least once per month.

The new year makes it more likely than ever before for aspiring entrepreneurs to start up their very own businesses without having studied entrepreneurship, because all you need now is basic computer skills and creativity (not degrees).

Drop a 💯if you agree!!

node.text:
Waiting for luck to fix your problems causes new problems, because no one ever made it from waiting around at home wishing.

You can visualize your success all your life but you never do anything about it- it's just dreaming. Take action and follow your dreams no matter what. For every word you say, you could take 2 actions and get it done.

Comment 🔥 if you agree

node.text:
For every failure in life, there is a lesson.

For every success person, there is a mentor.

For every circle, someone is out growing it.

For every human, there is a God giving talent and purpose.

It’s is up to you to see these opportunities in life, and do something about it. Don’t settle for being average when greatness is right on the other side. You can complain about not being where you want to be at in life, or make the choice to change it. Today!

Your life change starts here: MentorMeSpec.com

It’s two types of people in this world:

1. The person that thinks money doesn’t make you happy.

2. The person who that understands without money, your life is harder and a struggle.

When you have the right information to apply, from the right person, to get the right results — You then have the ability to create wealth. You can pass down the game and assets to your kids and family.

But the reality is... you can’t pass down broke.

To become the best, you must learn from the best.

Go to MentorMeSpec.com to join my apprentice program. I’m discounting the program for the next 24 hours for the first 100 people — before the price goes back up. 🖤

node.text:
If you only learn one thing from wealthy people this is it:

Being wealthy is rarely about luck

It’s not even about having tons of money

It’s about their mindset …

And how they rely on people to achieve their goals

It’s time to think like the wealthy 💯

node.text:
There's no point trying to become successful on your own. Trying to figure everything out by yourself and struggling by yourself. When someone has already made the mistakes you’re about to make, lost the money that you are about to lose. Learn from someone that has already been where you want to be in life. 

There is no lack of information, it’s only a lack of Accountability and guidance. When you are ready, God will put the right person in front of you but it’s up to you to take advantage of the opportunity.

You only get two life-changing opportunities in a lifetime. Make sure when they present themselves, you take that leap of faith.

Tag someone that needs to hear this message!

node.text:
In this era of social media and instant gratification, it's more lucrative than ever to start a digital business that caters to the needs of your target audience.

The best passive income business to jump into in 2021 is a digital one. The internet revolution has created an era where every company needs some sort of online presence, and this means that there are endless opportunities for the savvy entrepreneur with little capital. Entrepreneurs can have their own storefront on social media or create product-based content under Youtube's Partner Program--which only requires uploading quality videos at least once per month.

The new year makes it more likely than ever before for aspiring entrepreneurs to start up their very own businesses without having studied entrepreneurship, because all you need now is basic computer skills and creativity (not degrees).

Drop a 💯if you agree!!

It’s a beautiful day to make sacrifices for success.

When you’re willing to make sacrifices for your goals, there is no limit to what you can achieve.

Success is not a destination, it’s a journey. Don’t be afraid to give up things you may love to get there.

It’s time to stop dreaming and start doing. You have the skills, you have the drive, but something is missing. What if I told you that there was a way to get access to me as your experienced mentor who could help you create your business?

You don’t need any more excuses. It’s time for action! 

I’m a big believer in mentorship. I think it’s the best way to learn and grow as an entrepreneur. If you’re ready for me to mentor you. 

Let’s talk here 👉🏽 www.m.me/iamspectacular 

Ps: Only taking only 20 serious mentees in the next 24 hours. That’s willing to put in the work to create generational wealth for their families with my success formula.

Are you ready?

node.text:
I want you to focus on what matters the most. RIGHT NOW. Not the past. Not blaming your parents, spouse, previous traumas, etc.. To have the life you have always dreamed of will happen when you let go, forgive, and heal.

There’s a lesson to be learned in every tragedy. It’s not about what happens but more about how you respond to what happens.

I have trained myself to have a growth mindset and think of every situation as a cup half full and not half empty. When you go into situations, your first thought should not be “what’s the worst that can happen” but more of “what’s the best that can happen” but with knowing the worst.

Take risk, invest in yourself and think about what can go right instead of what can go wrong. Not what you will lose by investing but what you will lose by NOT investing.

Say AMEN if you agree! And why? Let me know your thoughts
